{# Intro + conference film. The portrait film is a self-hosted MP4, served
   same-origin from /assets/video/ so iOS plays it inline (GitHub Release
   assets are octet-stream + attachment, which iOS refuses). theme.js sets
   the src and muted-autoplays it only when it scrolls into view; it pauses
   off-screen, and prefers-reduced-motion gets native controls. #}
<section class="section" aria-labelledby="intro-2026-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="film-feature">
      <div class="film-feature-body">
        <div class="featured-eyebrow">In review</div>
        <h2 id="intro-2026-title">Two days in Stockholm</h2>
        <p>
          The 2026 European Security Studies Conference brought the community to Stockholm
          University for two days of panels and roundtables, jointly organised by the COST
          Action NetSec, the European Initiative for Security Studies (EISS), and Stockholm
          University.
        </p>
        <p>
          It was the first edition to carry the European Security Studies Conference (ESSC)
          name, as the network widened into a broader European partnership.
        </p>
        <p class="muted">
          A short film, shot and edited on site, captures the atmosphere across the venue.
        </p>
      </div>
      {%- set filmSrc = "/assets/video/essc-2026.mp4" -%}
      {%- set filmPoster = "/assets/images/8e43301e-7945-4a0c-aac2-04719ac702a8-800x450.jpg" -%}
      {%- set filmCaption = "ESSC 2026, Stockholm." -%}
      {% include "film-embed.njk" %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

